---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import TimeLineElement from "../components/cv/TimeLine.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Resume" sideBarActiveItemID="cv">
	<div class="mb-5">
		<div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Profile</div>
	</div>

	<div class="mb-10 text-justify">
		Former data analyst turned full-stack developer, bringing 7+ years of analytical experience to building
		user-focused web applications. Has built interactive client prototypes, remediated WCAG 2.1 AA accessibility
		issues, and shipped production features in Next.js. Also brings additional hands-on experience in Java and
		Spring Boot through personal projects.
	</div>

	<div class="mb-5">
		<div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Professional Experience</div>
	</div>

	<div class="time-line-container mb-10">
		<TimeLineElement title="Front-End Developer at BlueChannel, Inc." subtitle="August 2023 to Present - Remote">
			<p class="italic">
				Blue Channel is a boutique web development agency that provides custom web applications for clients
				across the US. As a contract frontend developer I assist clients with UI/UX features and prototyping.
			</p>
			<br />
			<ul class="list-disc mx-6">
				<li>
					Co-developed a 35+ screen interactive prototype for the Central Oregon Irrigation District's (COID)
					water rights application using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, collaborating with a PM across sprints and
					representing the team directly on client calls.
				</li>
				<li>
					Identified an opportunity to automate COID's manual data transfer process during a client call,
					surfacing a solution that reduced data transfer time from 3 weeks to less than 1 day.
				</li>
				<li>
					Conduct ongoing WCAG 2.1 AA accessibility audits across multiple client engagements, identifying and
					remediating critical compliance issues using WAVE and W3C tooling — work that began as a single
					project and expanded into a recurring agency service.
				</li>
				<!-- <li>Cornerstone is base template from big commerce (hosting provided), which uses handlebars and stencil CLI to start the project (separate package required to work with cornerstone) - Aarons says write I was exposed to SCSS (requires node package to complie down to regular CSS), handlebars and light JS. </li> -->
			</ul>
			<br />
		</TimeLineElement>
		<TimeLineElement title="Data Analyst at Deloitte" subtitle="August 2019 to May 2023 - McLean, Virginia">
			<p class="italic">
				Big four public accounting and consultancy firm where I focused on helping clients improve accuracy and
				time required for estimating a variety of tax return positions using statistical sampling.
			</p>
			<br />
			<ul class="list-disc mx-6">
				<li>
					Designed and evaluated statistical samples to help 700+ corporate clients estimate positions for
					federal and state tax returns.
				</li>
				<li>
					Developed a process efficiency script to reduce client tax research time by 10-20%, improving sample
					size efficiency while maintaining healthy relative precision.
				</li>
				<li>
					Assisted in expanding statistical sampling services across R&D and Inventory tax opportunities
					growing revenues by 10-15%.
				</li>
			</ul>
			<br />
		</TimeLineElement>
